-Hmm.

764
00:46:33,582 --> 00:46:37,377
And... they wanna sleep with us.

765
00:46:42,424 --> 00:46:44,426
Yeah, I thought it was a joke too.

766
00:46:44,510 --> 00:46:47,179
So--? So why are you showing me this?

767
00:46:50,891 --> 00:46:52,809
As a joke, obviously.

768
00:46:52,893 --> 00:46:53,810
Oh.

769
00:46:55,938 --> 00:46:58,148
