People go through rough patches.

772
00:47:03,028 --> 00:47:04,613
I don't wanna become...

773
00:47:06,073 --> 00:47:07,115
like my parents.

774
00:47:07,699 --> 00:47:11,370
They couldn't stay in love.

775
00:47:12,496 --> 00:47:14,498
Maybe we need to shake things up.

776
00:47:15,999 --> 00:47:18,585
It sounds crazy, but I read that article.

777
00:47:18,669 --> 00:47:19,795
[Joe] Opening our marriage.

778
00:47:19,878 --> 00:47:21,880
This loophole cannot be falling
into my lap.

779
00:47:21,964 --> 00:47:24,341
I don't even know how I feel about it.

780
00:47:24,424 --> 00:47:28,220
Sherry just said it was the greatest hack,

781
00:47:28,303 --> 00:47:31,014
and I guess...

782
00:47:32,057 --> 00:47:34,851
