786
00:47:40,524 --> 00:47:43,235
Love, Love, stop, stop, stop backpedaling.

787
00:47:45,112 --> 00:47:46,822
You can come to me with anything.

788
00:47:46,905 --> 00:47:49,575
That's what this marriage is, right?

789
00:47:50,158 --> 00:47:54,121
No idea is too crazy?
We talk things through, right?

790
00:47:55,247 --> 00:47:57,583
And we make decisions together.

791
00:48:02,004 --> 00:48:03,171
I love you.

792
00:48:09,136 --> 00:48:10,971
[Joe] And I love you.

793
